message.text:
𝐎𝐡—𝐡𝐢, 𝐤𝐚-𝐈𝐀𝐒! We are the 𝓛𝓮𝓰𝓪𝓵 𝓓𝓮𝓹𝓪𝓻𝓽𝓶𝓮𝓷𝓽 𝓸𝓯 𝓽𝓱𝓮 𝓘𝓐𝓢 𝓢𝓽𝓾𝓭𝓮𝓷𝓽 𝓒𝓸𝓾𝓷𝓬𝓲𝓵, and we are going to tell you why you should apply to our department. 

𝘿𝙤 𝙮𝙤𝙪 𝙬𝙖𝙣𝙩 𝙩𝙤 𝙛𝙚𝙚𝙡 𝙘𝙤𝙢𝙛𝙤𝙧𝙩𝙖𝙗𝙡𝙚 𝙪𝙨𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙡𝙚𝙜𝙖𝙡 𝙟𝙖𝙧𝙜𝙤𝙣 𝙞𝙣 𝙚𝙫𝙚𝙧𝙮𝙙𝙖𝙮 𝙡𝙞𝙛𝙚? As a member of the Legal Department, you will have the chance to be familiarized with both university and national policies that affect FEU students. With this, you will also learn how to review and craft legal documents, such as contracts, statements, governing documents, and many more! As you grow with us, you'll be able to remember hundreds of important details at the drop of a hat! 

So what are you waiting for, future lawyer?! 𝒯𝒶𝓇𝒶 𝓃𝒶 𝒶𝓉 𝒾𝓁𝒶𝒷𝒶𝓈 𝓂𝑜 𝒶𝓃𝑔 𝒾𝓎𝑜𝓃𝑔 𝒾𝓃𝓃𝑒𝓇 𝐸𝓁𝓁𝑒 𝒲𝑜𝑜𝒹𝓈💅🏼

📌JOIN IAS SC
https://forms.office.com/r/0RTuzxQ5rR

The field whispers, the season calls! Will you answer the call of peace? Come, bloom with us again tomorrow! ✨

message.text:
𝐏𝐄𝐀𝐂𝐄𝐭𝐚𝐡𝐚𝐧 𝐬𝐚 𝐏𝐈𝐘𝐔!🌾

Patuloy na Lumalago ang 𝐏𝐄𝐀𝐂𝐄𝐭𝐚𝐡𝐚𝐧 𝐬𝐚 𝐏𝐈𝐘𝐔!🌾

Day 2 was a blast! The root continues to grow as it thrives with harmony, compassion, and service. Different faces, different stories, but one purpose—— to lead with a heart and initiatives! Sama na sa pag-aani, future peaceliners!

The field whispers, the season calls! Will you answer the call of peace? Come, bloom with us again tomorrow! ✨ 

#KaPeacetahanNgAni
#TamHunt2025
#ACP3PeaceTAYO
